name: FakeValues_equalsTest
description: Unit tests for the equals method in the FakeValues class.

test_cases.name: testEquals_SameInstance
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with the same instance of FakeValues.

test_cases.name: testEquals_DifferentInstanceSameContext
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with different instances of FakeValues but with the same context.

test_cases.name: testEquals_DifferentContext
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with different instances of FakeValues and different contexts.

test_cases.name: testEquals_DifferentType
test_cases.description: Tests the equals method with a different type (not an instance of FakeValues).
